      "id": "PopularPost227267",
      "post_content": "@townend\\_GLS I believe you can as you are not targeting the creatures, which have shroud, but the cards which don't since they are not on the battlefield yet. The only abilities that function outside of the battlefield are those that specifically state that they do, or characteristic defining abilities, like P/T, color, type, subtype etc.",
